translate chinese epilogue_mi_872ed3da:


    "我抱着她，紧紧的搂住她。"


translate chinese epilogue_mi_85ff07ec:


    my "还没有..."


translate chinese epilogue_mi_a20cefa7_32:


    "..."


translate chinese epilogue_mi_f54fc1f7:


    "我坐下来，盯着远处的森林。"


